\nslope is recovered with an error of 36% for 50 images, and this improves to 10%\nfor 1000 images with Hubble Space Telescope-like noise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2020 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Oct 2021 19:12:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2022 17:47:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
